keycloak-kafka

This product includes software originally developed as "keycloak-kafka" by
SnuK87 (https://github.com/SnuK87/keycloak-kafka), licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0.

This repository is a fork maintained at
https://github.com/discostur/keycloak-kafka.

Modifications made in this fork include, among others:
  - Upgrade to Apache Kafka 4.2.x and Keycloak 26.5.x
  - KRaft-based docker-compose setup (ZooKeeper removed)
  - Expanded unit test coverage
  - Renamed Maven groupId and Java package namespace to com.github.discostur

